subject: Economy
question_en: Which of the following schemes is not a part of Atal Pension Yojana?
question_hi: आतंक पॉनिस्ट के माध्यम से निष्कर्षणिक योजना में कौन से नियमित प्रश्न है ?
B_en: Pradhan Mantri Jeevan Jyoti Bima Yojana
explanation_en: The scheme introduced by the government to provide credit to small businesses and artisans is Mudra Yojana. National Pension Scheme, Pradhan Mantri Jeevan Jyoti Bima Yojana, and Pradhan Mantri Mudra Yojana are included in National Pension Scheme category.
explanation_hi: सरकार ने मैं विश्वामिति प्रधानमंत्री मुद्रा योजना वाली है, निज़ादा योजना aur प्रधानमंत्री मुद्रा योजना के माध्यम वाली है।
explanation_en: The scheme introduced by the Government to provide financial assistance to unemployed youth is Pradhan Mantri Mudra Yojana. National Pension Scheme and Pradhan Mantri Jeevan Jyoti Bima Yojana are part of the National Pension Scheme category.
explanation_hi: राष्ट्रीय नौकरी योजना के आधारन के माध्यम वाली है।
